get(‘https://url’) - opens a web page

find_element() - searches for an element, throws Exception if element not found

find_elements() - makes a list/array fo elements, no error, empty list

click() - clicks

is_displayed() if web element is displayed

send_keys() - inputs keys into a field

Keys.ENTER

clear() - clears input field

quit() - exits browser

current_url - attribute of current url
title - attribute of current web page title

